  "text": "Big data tends to be defined in terms of its bigness (volume, velocity and variety etc.), and being too big for human analysts and conventional computing power to analyze [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, in reality, it blurs with many diverse uses, technologies and trends [CITATION_3] .",
